pull.title: [walletdb] Fix syntax error in key parser
pull.body:
This needs backport to all versions of bitcoin/altcoins after merge.

A dump may look like:

```
VERSION=3
format=bytevalue
database=main
type=btree
db_pagesize=4096
HEADER=END
<{Data}>
DATA=END
```

So the current parser gives us odd data like:

`keyHex="DATA=END";`
`valueHex="";`

(sometimes the other way round)
